But Fugawi kan be installed in Swedish-English or German language.

If you live outside Sweden just:
1. Install  fugawi4012.exe
2. Replace original exe with the one in "cracked exe" directory.

The other stuff i wrote is just how you install a mapengine for Swedish .rik maps.
